n or payment.

Here again the Google Books case seems pertinent, particularly given the ef=
fort and intentionality necessary to generate copyrighted content (and whic=
h has already been limited by OpenAI). The district judge wrote ( https://a=
rstechnica.com/tech-policy/2013/11/google-books-ruled-legal-in-massive-win-=
for-fair-use/ ) :

